#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_guides/security-jpa.adoc:91 upstream/_guides/security-jpa.adoc:116 upstream/_guides/security-jpa.adoc:141 upstream/_guides/security-jpa.adoc:168 upstream/_guides/security-jpa.adoc:235
